{"lemma":"ضَرْعِ","slug":"ضَرْعِ","root":"ض.ر.ع","root_slug":"ض-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25783","n25788","n25789","n25790","n25791"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be low, to be abased"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to plea humbly, to pray","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of ضَرِعَ (ḍariʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"udder, tit"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"similar"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25783","headword_ar":"ضَرَعَ","root":"DrE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", said of a lamb or kid,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his mouth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroE","text_ar":"ضَرْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dug"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his mother."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [This seems to be regarded by some as the primary signification.] ―         -b2-  And (TA) the same, (S, Msb, K,) said of a man, (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEa","text_ar":"ضَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaruEa","text_ar":"ضَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) inf. n. (S, Msb, K) of the first (S, Msb, TA) and of the third (TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAEapN","text_ar":"ضَرَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S Msb, K,) and (K) of the second (TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, lowly, humble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submissive;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low, abject,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abased;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEa","text_ar":"ضَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lowered, humbled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abased, himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tDr~E","text_ar":"تضرّع"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is more commonly used in this sense,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and made petition for a gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaruEa","text_ar":"ضَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAEapN","text_ar":"ضَرَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and it is said that the verb in this last sense is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense expl. in the first sentence: so in the “ Mufradát ” [of Er-Rághib]:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEa","text_ar":"ضَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", likewise, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in measure], signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak in body, slender, spare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light of flesh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuruwEN","text_ar":"ضُرُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app. as an inf. n. of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) For another explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAEapN","text_ar":"ضَرَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", see 5. ―         -b3-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is made trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":":] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa bihi farasuhu","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ بِهِ فَرَسُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His horse humbled him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abased him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) or, as in the L,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcame him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEa minohu","text_ar":"ضَرَعَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of an animal of prey, (IKtt, K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuruwEN","text_ar":"ضُرُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He approached"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a man, (IKtt, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a thing. (K.) ―         -b5-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["TA","S","Msb","K","O","IKtt"]},{"entry_id":"n25788","headword_ar":"ضَرْعٌ","root":"DrE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a word of well-known meaning; (TA;) [properly and generally, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"udder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but sometimes applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dug,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroE","text_ar":"ضَرْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of every female that has a cloven hoof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the she-camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of each of these:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the former only;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat and of the cow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"that of the camel being termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lth, O, K:) it is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the clovenhoofed female, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vadoY","text_ar":"ثَدْى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to cattle, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vadoY","text_ar":"ثَدْى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Towsheeh, TA:) accord. to the IF, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of other animals:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to IDrd,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"only"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: AZ says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it comprises the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaA='","text_ar":"اَطْبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolaAf","text_ar":"اَخْلَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in which are the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHaAliyl","text_ar":"اَحَالِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are the orifices for the passing forth of the milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuruwEN","text_ar":"ضُرُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu zaroEN walaA DaroEN","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ زَرْعٌ وَلَا ضَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not seed-produce nor an udder"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has not anything:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has not land to sow, nor ewe"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-goat"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other animal having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroE","text_ar":"ضَرْع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Lth","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25789","headword_ar":"ضِرْعٌ","root":"DrE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A like; a similar person"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroEN","text_ar":"ضَرْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SrE","text_ar":"صرع"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiroEN","text_ar":"صِرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaroEN","text_ar":"صَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O and K and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SrE","text_ar":"صرع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sort,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state, condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner of being:"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1788},{"kind":"text","text":"thing: as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaroEN","text_ar":"ضَرْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiroEN","text_ar":"صِرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaroEN","text_ar":"صَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SrE","text_ar":"صرع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strand of a rope:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiroEN","text_ar":"صِرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuruwEN","text_ar":"ضُرُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K: and the CK adds"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDoruEN","text_ar":"اَضْرُعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n25790","headword_ar":"ضَرَعٌ","root":"DrE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lowly, humble, submissive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of abasement;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally an inf. n., and therefore, as an epithet,] applied to a single person and to a pl. number: (O:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAriEN","text_ar":"ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, applied to a single person; (O, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotaDoriEN","text_ar":"مُسْتَضْرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, *TA:) accord. To Lth, one says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xad~uka DaAriEN","text_ar":"خَدُّكَ ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDoraEu","text_ar":"اَضْرَعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the same, (Ham p. 344,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobuka DaAriEN","text_ar":"جَنْبُكَ ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [meaning, as is implied in the O,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy cheek is lowly"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., and so"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the like is said in the Ham p. 590,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anota DaAriEN","text_ar":"اَنْتَ ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art lowly"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (O:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAriEN","text_ar":"ضَارِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEapN","text_ar":"ضَرَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuruwEN","text_ar":"ضُرُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAriEN","text_ar":"ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies, and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEN","text_ar":"ضَرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and [in an intensive sense] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaruwEN","text_ar":"ضَرُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEapN","text_ar":"ضَرَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowering, humbling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abasing, himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thus, and making petition for a gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEN","text_ar":"ضَرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) the former (Msb, K) originally an inf. n. (Msb) [and therefore, as an epithet,] applied to a single person and to a pl. number: (K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAriEN","text_ar":"ضَارِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to anything: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small in age, weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and lean, spare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light of flesh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljisomi","text_ar":"الجِسْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAriEu","text_ar":"ضَارِعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariEN","text_ar":"ضَرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean, spare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light of flesh, and weak, in the body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) applied to a man: (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a colt,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not having strength to run,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of the smallness of his age."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cowardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak-hearted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa waraEN DaraEN","text_ar":"هُوَ وَرَعٌ ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[both app. meaning the same]. (TA.) And, applied to a man, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inexperienced in affairs; ignorant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in whom is no profit nor judgment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumorN","text_ar":"غُمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA","K","S","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n25791","headword_ar":"ضَرِعٌ","root":"DrE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraEN","text_ar":"ضَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}